title: 790 Picnic Time Monaco Beach Chair
transcripts: The Monaco beach chair by Picnic Time is a low lightweight portable chair that provides comfortable, reclined seating when your on the go. It features a chair-back with six support positions and sits eleven inches off the ground. Made of durable polyester on a lightweight aluminum frame, the Monaco beach chair features a comfortable pillow for head and neck support. and a sturdy integrated cup holder in the arm rest that ensures you can always have your favorite refreshment at hand. The Monaco comes in a variety of colors and has a maximum weight capacity of 300 pounds. Convenient backpack straps free your hands so you can carry other items to your destination. Rest and relaxation comes easy in the Monaco beach chair.
